comment:
With every song from –û–∫–µ–∞–Ω –ï–ª—å–∑–∏ I read through the comments. What surprises me every time is that all comments are in Ukrainian. As if there is nobody outside of Ukraine interested or know about this beautiful band or about Ukraine itself and it' s people for that matter.
Since a long time I found myself to be interested in Ukraine and a few weeks ago I was there for the first time. I will never forget it. I was in Lviv, where this video was shot I think and the Carpathians. I am so glad and proud I could meet the Ukrainian people. You are so beautiful. You are a proud people. You may all have different opinions, different religions, different needs, different wishes but when there is this moment of trouble, you find each other, you become one. One people, one entity. I have seen it happen. It is beautiful. Be proud. I love you all and will come back. meanwhile, please care for each other.
